{"tid":759982,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔仔會不會叫?","createTime":"2018-07-29T06:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T06:43:25.000Z","uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eeee16d65c7fd5e4862af6769b704d23e8802562","tid":759982,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子會叫的。不滿的時候會咕咕叫。後腳大力踏地代表不滿，但也可以代表驚慌覺得有危險，要看當時的情況。在大自然內，兔子後腳大力踏地是用來警告其他兔仔(包括你)有危險。當兔子遇到巨大驚慌或痛苦也會尖叫，例如被捕獵者(predatory animals)追殺和吃的時候，當然這情況是很慘。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下video 可以看到兔仔咕咕叫。當牠用鼻碰主人的手然後縮低代表想被撫摸:</strong> </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ8wfR7k3844&d=l529D9%2FMuNwcFbTqbOpFY0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=def5c44e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更多關於兔子身體語言(害怕、開心、憂愁、憤怒）：<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=l529D9%2FMuNwcFbTqbOpFY0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=68910ef8\" target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a></span>"}]}